liblasx2lsx (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Pure C emulation for all ~700 LASX instructions.
  * JIT translation to LSX (128-bit) with use-def optimization.
  * Loop detection and xvmap-based loop JIT.

 -- liblasx2lsx contributors  <noreply@example.com>  Mon, 11 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800
